juniDs1Agent.name: juniDs1Agent

revisions.description: DS1-MIB: Replaced SMIv1 'groups' (RFC1406-MIB) with SMIv2 conformance groups (DS1-MIB).
Juniper-DS1-MIB: Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names.
Juniper-DS1-MIB: Added support for FDL transmit mode, remote FDL strings and far end FDL carrier.
DS1-MIB: Added far end statistics support. Juniper-DS1-MIB: Added far end statistics support. Added FDL support.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniDs1Agent.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886-3146 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@Juniper.net
juniDs1Agent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the DS1 component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniDs1AgentV1.name: juniDs1AgentV1
juniDs1AgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the DS1 component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DS1 component was supported in JUNOSe 1.0 system releases.
juniDs1AgentV1.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS1 application in JUNOSe. This version became obsolete when new objects were added to the Juniper-DS1-MIB.

juniDs1AgentV2.name: juniDs1AgentV2
juniDs1AgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the DS1 component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DS1 component was supported in JUNOSe 1.1 thru JUNOSe 2.x system
        releases.
juniDs1AgentV2.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS1 application in JUNOSe. This version became obsolete when dynamic DS1 interface support was added to the Juniper-DS1-MIB.

juniDs1AgentV3.name: juniDs1AgentV3
juniDs1AgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the DS1 component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DS1 component was supported in JUNOSe 3.x system releases.
juniDs1AgentV3.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS1 application in JUNOSe. This version became obsolete when far end statistics support was added and FDL support was added to the Juniper-DS1-MIB.

juniDs1AgentV4.name: juniDs1AgentV4
juniDs1AgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the DS1 component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DS1 component was supported in JUNOSe 4.0 system releases.
juniDs1AgentV4.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS1 application in JUNOSe. This version became obsolete when more FDL support was added to the Juniper-DS1-MIB.

juniDs1AgentV5.name: juniDs1AgentV5
juniDs1AgentV5.productrelease:
Version 5 of the DS1 component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version
        of the DS1 component is supported in JUNOSe 4.1 and subsequent system
        releases.
juniDs1AgentV5.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DS1 application in JUNOSe.
